name: "fino, leo esta fino"
description:
"tropical boom bap" is a collection based on portraits of argentinian and other latin american artists with 3a5a1a style. 20 eds each artwork.

"fino, leo esta fino" shows a classic image of leo mattioli, an argentinian singer of cumbia santafesina who left us in 2011, in a fancy versace outfit with a casio watch special edition 3a5a1a and a very stylish gucci hat. in his hands a fernet with coke and a romantic rose, in his neck his characteristic phrase and gold, a lot of gold, because that's what the lion was, gold. long life 2 leo.
